```mermaid
flowchart TB
    %% Client Side
    User[User Browser]

    %% Network Services
    DNS[DNS Provider]
    CDN[CDN / Edge Network]

    %% GitHub Platform
    GitHub[GitHub Platform]
    Repo[GitHub Repository]
    Actions[GitHub Actions CI/CD]
    Pages[GitHub Pages Hosting]

    %% Build Artifacts
    Build[Static Site Artifacts]

    %% Connections
    User -->|HTTPS (TCP/IP)| DNS
    DNS -->|DNS (UDP/TCP)| CDN
    CDN -->|HTTPS (TLS over TCP)| Pages

    %% GitHub Workflow
    Developer[Developer]
    Developer -->|Git Push (HTTPS or SSH)| Repo
    Repo -->|Webhook (HTTPS)| Actions
    Actions -->|Build & Deploy (HTTPS)| Pages
    Pages --> Build

    %% CDN Caching
    Pages -->|HTTPS| CDN

    %% Protocol Annotations
    subgraph Network_Layer
        TCP[TCP/IP]
        UDP[UDP]
    end

    subgraph Application_Layer
        HTTPS[HTTPS]
        DNS_PROTO[DNS]
        SSH[SSH]
        HTTP_API[REST / Webhooks]
    end
```
